<text top="1319" left="52" width="677" height="50" font="font3" id="p1_t16" reading_order_no="15" segment_no="10" tag_type="text">Females  are  endowed  with  less  alcohol  de- </text>
<text top="1363" left="52" width="677" height="49" font="font4" id="p1_t17" reading_order_no="16" segment_no="10" tag_type="text">hydrogenase—the  first  enzyme  in  the  stom- </text>
